nt, the signatore has the option of forwarding the report without comment, sending the report back to the investigating officer for additional work, or forwarding it `` as is'' and express his disagreement with some or all of the material. `` I'm not implying that anyone has done any of those things yet,'' <PERSON> Williams </PERSON> said. A <ORGANIZATION> Navy </ORGANIZATION> source, who spoke on condition he not be identified, said it is expected that each level of command will take about a week to go over the report. `` It wo n't get here before August,'' said the source.
